{"id": 2051, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X潘多拉】你都经历过哪些“满分”/“不及格”的告白？", "description": "我喜欢你。你喜欢我吗？", "record_count": 8937, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171207193755FEpQBP23cOdKYjlu.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-07T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 253184, "content": "告白都是在一起之后的情话啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 253185, "content": "表白有什么可怕，请你不怕为难不要拐弯", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614051}, {"id": 253186, "content": "希望遇到一个人，喜欢到让我鼓足勇气主动告白", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187317}, {"id": 253188, "content": "太长了懒得说", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993046}, {"id": 253189, "content": "初三的时候，来了一位新同学，离毕业还有五十多天，她通过QQ向我表白，但在那之前我和她却没有怎么说过话，当时很意外。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066771}, {"id": 253190, "content": "QQ匿名悄悄话  说了一大堆 问了又不承认", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173909}, {"id": 259334, "content": "“不如我泡你吧？”\n\n当时就在想这人的脑子 ? 是不是有坑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230056}, {"id": 253191, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1203950}, {"id": 253959, "content": "我也欢喜你好久了，如果一切都刚刚好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209955}, {"id": 253192, "content": "从小到大，喜欢我的我不喜欢，表白了大家都尴尬；我喜欢的不喜欢我，面都见不到表白个毛。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1120654}, {"id": 253448, "content": "没有，滚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680656}, {"id": 253193, "content": "一封毫无文笔可言的信，加插在门上的玫瑰，但他并不知道我小学就已经看上他了.", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206520}, {"id": 253194, "content": "我是个滥情的人，只能被表白。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202158}, {"id": 253195, "content": "不喜欢微信QQ表白，也不喜欢没有表白的暧昧，我喜欢有勇气当面跟我告白的人，可是目前没有。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201122}, {"id": 253197, "content": "企鹅账号发给我一串数学(962464)，当时没有手机(很low)，然后我问什么意思，她也不说，后来有了喜欢的人以后才恍然大悟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883037}, {"id": 253198, "content": "没有 都是表白别人惨被拒 如果非要说 最喜欢直球式 坦诚而勇敢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172225}, {"id": 253199, "content": "你不明白你这问题有多伤吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128361}, {"id": 253200, "content": "是我先告的白啊。这怎么好意思说出口……", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205893}, {"id": 253201, "content": "现在哪来什么表白，都是一些似有若无的乱撩", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108569}, {"id": 253457, "content": "无语", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202327}, {"id": 253202, "content": "怀疑以前谈的都是假恋爱 以下如此浪漫的告白没有经历过 帮别人倒是摆过蜡烛…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206614}, {"id": 253203, "content": "那个不认为男生需要先表白的：很多女生也不认为应该先表白?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759228}, {"id": 253204, "content": "喜欢上了一个比自己小4岁的男生?惨遭拒绝  他给我来句他不是适合当我的男朋友。这句话，怎么理解?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206685}, {"id": 253460, "content": "我初中的一个同桌，我们关系是有点暧昧的。一个周六我在QQ空间看到他公布了个恋情，周日晚自习，我八卦一下他说是网恋。周二吧，他又说分了，上课时学到“dear”这个词，然后他就老是对我说，下午一节课上，他给我传张字条写着“做我女朋友吗？”我回避。他追问，我只能说拒绝。因为我们才14。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208317}, {"id": 253205, "content": "行吧 拉黑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098949}, {"id": 254741, "content": "那个 要不要一起睡觉什么的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215484}, {"id": 253206, "content": "告白完，自此没有后话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206705}, {"id": 253462, "content": "QQ表白 两次 .吓卸Q 两次...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202368}, {"id": 253207, "content": "主要看脸，不好看的说什么都白搭，好看的说hello也像表白", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963953}, {"id": 253208, "content": "那天你迎风穿过操场，我站在乒乓球台，被你的样子所吸引。??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168129}, {"id": 253209, "content": "明明不熟的人，非要强行关心别人，搞得很了解我一样。典型的交浅言深，极其尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931751}, {"id": 254745, "content": "QQ和QQ匿名两边在聊，过了一会儿才说穿，然后⋯成功了", "image": "img/option/option/20171217183553ndiHfJLeG2hwCFK5.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242684}, {"id": 253210, "content": "我是男生，但依然反对那种发消息式的表白，最起码你和她语音吧，单纯文字上的，还是算了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145289}, {"id": 253211, "content": "你长得好像我前女友哦，我发照片给你看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855687}, {"id": 253469, "content": "没有告白过\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208410}, {"id": 253472, "content": "本人是个女生。初中晚自习同桌（男生）忽然传纸条问我：喜欢一个女生，但不知道怎么处理和她的关系。我：先从好朋友作起吧。他：难啊。曾经怕绯闻都不敢和她说话…准备期末考过她就去告白。我：她成绩好吗？他：你别想套我话。我：我保证不会告诉她。他：可是告诉你之后“她”就知道了啊。我瞬间脸红", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208434}, {"id": 253736, "content": "没有\n我们结婚后我会对你很好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210083}, {"id": 253227, "content": "看着看着突然就扎心了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206848}, {"id": 253483, "content": "在qq上说了无数遍如何如何喜欢我，可到了生活中也没见对我有多好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190926}, {"id": 253231, "content": "就是在一起", "image": "img/option/option/20171208113743Kn1ZS4T3rEpjbC0X.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406438}, {"id": 253233, "content": "还真的就叫不醒一个假睡的人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059243}, {"id": 253234, "content": " 我想保护你，做我女朋友吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 877180}, {"id": 252983, "content": "只收到过不感兴趣的滥情人的廉价告白，喜欢的人怎么会告白我呢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 240, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879838}, {"id": 252984, "content": "没有过，一次也没有过", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793207}, {"id": 255800, "content": "好好当贵族不好吗，告什么白", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219371}, {"id": 252985, "content": "没有\n下一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 1684, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770585}, {"id": 252986, "content": "凌晨收到QQ信息：说喜欢我。我第二天上午才看到，回复了婉转拒绝的短信。在表白这件事上请直接干脆一点，QQ、微信的就免了吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 488, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2362}, {"id": 253242, "content": "当面告白满分\n社交软件负分", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140458}, {"id": 252987, "content": "没有被表白过啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809679}, {"id": 254011, "content": "马路边上吼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211896}]}